: : Rodimus Prime : :

Just after Magnus tells Rodimus that Optimus is coming, Hydras yells, causing Rodimus to turn to him.

Rodimus saw Cygnar&#39;s body slumped on the ground, limp, and in flames. A look of unbelievable anger flew through Rodimus&#39; face.

Rodimus Prime: Cygnar! I&#39;ll get you Hydras, you bastard!

Rodimus runs right at Hydras, and attempts to tackle him.

Rodimus Prime: You wanted me, and now you got me... GALVATRON!

Rodimus was in a rage over everything. The death of Cygnar, the situation on Cybertron, the coming of Optimus, and the renewed feud with Galvatron.

The only way that Rodimus was holding on to any sanity was the thought of protecting Nightlight.

